gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<br />\n我諗佢唔可以<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/fozen_smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n屌你點解乜都知<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n唉我諗呢兩日去旅行社睇package算 <br />\n台北機票酒店預每人5000算<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<br />\n拿拿聲book好過啦<br />\n<br />\n洗錢有乜好驚<br />\n搵唔返我就真係驚<br />\n<br />\n既然冇得避免<br />\n早d settle好開心玩<br />\n唔通煩一大輪可以俾少d咩？<br />\n<br />\n俾錢啦，唔好等。 <img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/fozen_smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"c0d670925633d7e2aeb5120e1f8b533917f957ef","tid":481711,"uid":106,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-28T15:56:07.000Z","msg":"2千蚊機票一個人都貴？假期喎大佬"},{"pid":"33b74aaf8a3de4c64c364e39baf37c459d995887","tid":481711,"uid":36157,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-28T15:57:27.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote>既然呢個價你俾唔落手, 你不如而家試下夾新年同復活節仲好啦<br />\n你硬食呢個價, 去到時咪又係一路玩一路屌, 開心咩<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 比人強逼硬食</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n咁你又唔好咁諗<br />\n你有緊嘅負擔（負累又好乜都好啦）<br />\n幾多人想有都冇？<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: x-small;\">（走來連登招絲跟著去三唔識七同床都有啦）</span>"},{"pid":"63f38ce14772d55341372c9bb6d568c07af10d7a","tid":481711,"uid":135896,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-29T02:25:53.000Z","msg":"旺季想平，就去歐洲啦，有俄航，中航⋯⋯轉一轉嘅都係16-17個鐘，果段時間同你check過，去瑞士蘇黎世搭中航，北京轉機，連稅唔使＄4000/1個<br />\n<br />\n仲去台北做乜"},{"pid":"f4a1c1853814d0f5171ca1e0c276b1107c0145be","tid":481711,"uid":11254,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"c